name: DenseNet-201 for Image Classification
full_description: DenseNet-201 is a densely connected convolutional neural network architecture designed for image classification tasks. Introduced in the paper 'Densely Connected Convolutional Networks' by Gao Huang et al., DenseNet-201 leverages dense connections between layers to improve information flow and gradient propagation, enabling the training of very deep networks with enhanced accuracy and efficiency.
keywords: image classification, deep learning, DenseNet-201, densely connected networks, computer vision
author: David Kim

ai_model.name: DenseNet-201
ai_model.description: A densely connected convolutional neural network model designed for high-accuracy image classification.
